headline: Herschel Walker: No one 'trusts' Biden; says he's running for Senate to restore trust in America
author: Fox News Staff
sentences: You know, right now with this new variant coming out, and you know, I think the biggest problem now is, you know, we're not energy independent And you talked about the chicken business a few minutes ago.
That's the reason I'm running for this Senate seat, because I want to bring some trust back to this country - the greatest country in the world.
Your price of everything is going up, and you know, you look what he did in Afghanistan and no one wants to talk about that anymore.
But do the military trust in him, do all the police trust in their people that lead in their cities?
HERSCHEL WALKER: I don't think anyone really trusts this administration.
Well, I'm in that business and the supply line is going down.
Where is the trust in the administration anymore?
